    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
