      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65B40 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This unit exhibits excellent compression across all cylinders and has had the critical rod bearing service performed with VAC coated bearings. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile, precise throws, paired with a clutch that retains strong clamping force. The chassis is dialed in with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and shows no signs of subframe fatigue. While the exterior displays minor stone peppering and road patina, the powertrain remains visceral, reaching its 8,400 RPM redline with the signature induction note of the individual throttle bodies. This is a robust, driver-quality example with a clear maintenance trajectory, perfect for those who prioritize longitudinal and lateral performance over a concours finish.",
